ler outperforms both ML and traditional (non-ML) AoI\nschedulers, such as, Deep Q Network (DQN)-based AoI Scheduler, Maximal Age\nFirst-Maximal Age Difference (MAF-MAD), MAF (Maximal Age First) , and\nround-robin in all considered practical scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2022 17:47:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Aug 2022 15:51:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 25 Apr 2023 15:32:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-26"}
