 this work strengthens\nthe hypothesis of Junkermeier et al.'s hypothesis that Du et al. synthesized\n3-carbophene and not graphenylene.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Mar 2022 04:57:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-10"}
