ry surface. Together, these\nresults indicate a great potential of ES-IBD for applications in structural\nbiology, but also outline the challenges that need to be solved for it to reach\nits full potential.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Mar 2022 12:24:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2022 11:19:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 21 Mar 2022 16:41:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
