lting in a more localised\npressure perturbation. These effects are not observed in VMEC, because closed\nmagnetic flux surfaces are enforced. Despite the sensitivity of JOREK results\non the assumed resistivity, saturated states can be found using both approaches\nthat are in reasonable agreement, even for this more advanced case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Mar 2022 14:46:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Jun 2022 15:41:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-20"}
